### Phase 3 — Supplier Management (Website Dashboard)

**Files to create/modify:**
- `components/DashboardInventory.tsx` — new component, added as tab in `dashboard.tsx`
- Tab structure: **Items | Invoices | Suppliers | Transfers**

**Suppliers tab features:**
- List all suppliers: name, contact, phone, email, payment terms
- Add / edit / delete supplier
- Click supplier → invoice history for that supplier
  - Sortable columns: Date, Invoice #, Subtotal, Tax, Fees, Discounts, Total, Status
  - Filter by: date range, category, paid/unpaid
  - Mark invoice as paid button
  - Total spend summary at top

**Items tab features:**
- Full inventory list with search + filter by category, location, low stock
- Edit item: name, category, size, unit, par level, default supplier
- Merge duplicates: admin selects two items → merge into one (quantities summed, history preserved)
- Low stock indicator: red badge when `location_inventory.quantity < inventory_items.par_level`

**Invoices tab features:**
- All invoices across all suppliers
- Filter by: date range, supplier, location, status
- Click to expand line items
- Mark as paid

**Transfers tab features:**
- Log a transfer: select from-location, to-location, item, quantity
- History of all transfers with date, item, qty, who transferred

---

### Phase 4 — Par Levels & Start of Day Integration

**Par level logic:**
- `par_level` on `inventory_items` — set by owner/manager via Items tab
- Low stock alert: `location_inventory.quantity < inventory_items.par_level`
- Alert surfaces: dashboard overview card, Inventory tab badge, Start of Day report

**Start of Day report changes (`reports` table, `type: 'daily'`):**
- Report `data` JSONB now includes inventory snapshot: `{ items: [{ name, quantity, par_level, below_par }] }`
- Items below par highlighted in report view
- "Add to shopping list" button per flagged item (saves to a `shopping_list` array in report data)
- Par level "checked" flag resets on SoD generation: `par_reset_on_sod = true` items get a `last_checked_at` timestamp

**App changes needed:**
- `StartOfDayReportScreen.tsx` — add inventory section showing par level status
- `ReportsScreen.tsx` — already being overhauled (see Reports overhaul task above); inventory section added there

